### Step 1: Update CSS for Animations
Add a transition effect to your `.circular-menu` class and modify the size for the expanded state.

```css
.circular-menu {
  position: relative;
  width: 100px; /* Start small */
  height: 100px; 
  border-radius: 50%;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: width 0.3s ease, height 0.3s ease;
