circularMenu.addEventListener('click', function() {
  circularMenu.classList.toggle('expanded');
});
```

### Step 3: Animation for Menu Items
To enhance it further, you can animate the menu items as they appear/disappear.

```css
.menu-item {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, opacity 0.3s ease;
  opacity: 0; /* Start invisible */
}

.circular-menu.expanded .menu-item {
  opacity: 1; /* Fade in */
}

/* Add a delay in transforming each item for staggered effects */
.menu-item:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.1s; }
.menu-item:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
.menu-item:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
.menu-item:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.4s; }
```

### Summary
1. The `.circular-menu` expands on click.
2. The `.menu-item` elements fade in due to an opacity transition.
3. You can adjust the timing and delay for a staggered effect.

This setup will create a nice expanding/contracting effect for your circular menu, similar to the dynamic feel of the ping system in League of Legends! Feel free to customize further!

